]}, {\"sentence\": \"In one video featuring Taiwaneseathleteswinning gold on the podium, a fan in the background could be seen having a sign snatched away.\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 653, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Taiwan's foreign ministry said it \\\"strongly condemns the crude and despicable means of malicious individuals ruthlessly snatching the 'Go Taiwan' slogan\\\".\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 809, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 655, \"end\": 661, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Free_area_of_the_Republic_of_China\", \"score\": 0.6074561462003818, \"rank\": 0.6460924260461889, \"text\": \"Taiwan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Free_area_of_the_Republic_of_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Free_area_of_the_Republic_of_China\"}, {\"begin\": 793, \"end\": 799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Free_area_of_the_Republic_of_China\", \"score\": 0.6074561462003818, \"rank\": 0.6460924260461889, \"text\": \"Taiwan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Free_area_of_the_Republic_of_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Free_area_of_the_Republic_of_China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ministry went on to describe the incident as violent and an act that \\\"violates the rule of law and infringes on freedom of speech\\\".\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 946, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Signs displaying political messages are banned at theOlympic Gamesbut many were left wondering why the word Taiwan is restricted.\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 1077, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1056, \"end\": 1062, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Free_area_of_the_Republic_of_China\", \"score\": 0.6074561462003818, \"rank\": 0.6460924260461889, \"text\": \"Taiwan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Free_area_of_the_Republic_of_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Free_area_of_the_Republic_of_China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's what you need to know.\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1107, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The word Taiwan is not explicitly banned from the Olympics but it is restricted in many ways.\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1202, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1118, \"end\": 1124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Free_area_of_the_Republic_of_China\", \"score\": 0.6074561462003818, \"rank\": 0.6460924260461889, \"text\": \"Taiwan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Free_area_of_the_Republic_of_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Free_area_of_the_Republic_of_China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Its flag is also banned from the Games, alongside those of Belarus and Russia.\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1281, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1262, \"end\": 1269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus\", \"score\": 0.9999999985147952, \"rank\": 1.3187116460144968e-09, \"text\": \"Belarus\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus\"}, {\"begin\": 1274, \"end\": 1280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999968486044598, \"rank\": 2.4627540485879304e-06, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But why?\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1290, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"China's controversial super-embassy in London is given go-ahead by Government  Government faces legal challenge if it approves China super-embassy  Kemi Badenoch joins protesters calling for Government to stop China mega-embassy  The best destinations and activities to book this winter  Taiwan has had a separate government fromChinasince 1949 and has its own constitution and democratically elected leaders.\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1701, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1292, \"end\": 1297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_C