ors.\", \"from\": 2798, \"to\": 2919, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2809, \"end\": 2815, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Free_area_of_the_Republic_of_China\", \"score\": 0.6074561462003818, \"rank\": 0.6460924260461889, \"text\": \"Taiwan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Free_area_of_the_Republic_of_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Free_area_of_the_Republic_of_China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  5  Football  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\", \"from\": 2921, \"to\": 3799, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2981, \"end\": 2990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9999030823084571, \"rank\": 9.692514308372942e-05, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\"}, {\"begin\": 3081, \"end\": 3090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9999030823084571, \"rank\": 9.692514308372942e-05, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/re